Checklist.txt.data:
📌Current work
____ Interface
    ✅ More icons for the default "Plexos Hyper" theme
    ✅ Metafile creation UX/UI
    ✅ LinkPreview meta creator integration
    ▶️ File properties window
    🔼 Task persistent popups

📌Recent work
____ Context Menu
    ✅ Simplify abysmal context menu logic
    ✅ Nest menu functions inside class
    ✅ Context menu templates stored in virtual file
    ✳️ Construct menus through static classes

____ Applications
    ✅ Reorganize application files and resources
    ✅ Update lau files for new window UI and icon arguments
    ✅ Popup app vastly improved

____ Windows
    ✅ Redesign window header for flexible button container
    ✅ Expect array of buttons in UI parameter
    ✅ Display opened file icon in access apps windows

____ Properties
    ✅ Redesign of grid settings window
    ✅ Grid settings app fully complete, with "accept/cancel/apply" logic
    ✅ Settings app works with both a cfg object and its file source
    🔼 Repurpose settings window for property window

____ Components
    ✅ New component class to handle multiple task components
    ✅ Node getter functions
    ✅ Did away with ridiculous replacementPair solution for arguments
    ✅ Code parser and highlighter component
    ⏯️ Custom scrollbar component

____ System
    ✅ Script import overhaul, now impmented through ES6 module imports
    ✅ Everything is scoped through modules now, no more global garbage

📌Requirements for 1.0 release
____ Notepad App
    ⏯️ Alt menu bar
    🟦 Do you want to save changes to Untitled? 
    🟦 Save - Don't Save - Cancel

____ Code Inspector App
    ⏯️ Alt menu bar
    🟦 HTML, CSS and JS notation colouring

____ Explorer App
    🔽 Alt menu bar
    🟦 Side navigation bar
    🟦 Open file explorer
    🟦 Save file explorer
    🔼 Backwards and forwards buttons
    🔼 Edit address bar
    🔼 Search bar
    🔼 Views

____ Settings App
    🟦 System settings
    🟦 Style settings
    🟦 Audio settings
    ⏯️ Desktop settings
    🟦 Application settings
    🟦 File settings

____ Taskbar
    🟦 Window tray
    🟦 Task tray
    🟦 Start menu
    🟦 Stash viewer
    🟦 Time / Date
    🟦 Volume
    🟦 Place on either border

____ Windows
    🔼 Maximize
    🔽 Minimize
    🔼 Check for out of bounds header
    🔼 Generate comfortable starting position
    🔼 Remember window size and position per task

____ Metafiles
    ✅ New Metafile - Metadata
    ✅ Insert URL - Type drop-down menu
    🟦 Pasting URL immediately creates Metafile

____ Metafile types
    ☑️ Webpage (.url)
    ☑️ Video (.vid)
    ☑️ Audio (.aud)
    ☑️ Image (.img)
    ☑️ Download (.dl)

____ Applications
    🟦 Framer
    🟦 Meta Media Player
    🟦 Image Viewer
    🟦 Properties

____ JSON files
    ✳️ Turn config into JSON file
    🟦 Make JSON editor app
    🟦 Virtualize JSON to represent its object reference

____ Other files
    ⏯️ JS files
    🟦 CSS files
    🟦 HTML files
    🟦 Shortcut files

____ Filesystem
    🟦 Virtualize all system files
    🟦 Trash and Stash
    ☑️ Select new vertex (reassign desktop directory) 
    🟦 Move files
    ☑️ Save storage state to core JSON 
    ☑️ Load storage state from core JSON 

____ LocalStorage
    🟦 Save on each change
    🟦 Measure remaining available space

____ Misc
    🟦 About HTML
